(9, 'Axborot –resurs markazimizda yangi adabiyot taqdimoti.', 'axborot-resurs-markazimizda-yangi-adabiyot-taqdimoti', '<p>Chirchiq davlat pedagogika instituti  dotsent v.b.Sultanov Xaytboy Eraliyevich “Tasviriy san’at va muhandislik grafikasi”</p>', '<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Chirchiq davlat pedagogika instituti &nbsp;dotsent v.b.Sultanov Xaytboy Eraliyevich “Tasviriy san’at va muhandislik grafikasi”</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"http://cspi.uz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/1_5.jpg\" style=\"width: 613.997px; height: 906.09px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"><img src=\"http://scpi.qnb.uz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/2_23.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 842.5px;\" class=\"fr-fic oc-img-bordered fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"http://cspi.uz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/4_13.jpg\" style=\"width: 616.99px; height: 934.644px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"http://cspi.uz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/5_7.jpg\" style=\"width: 615px; height: 868.118px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"http://cspi.uz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/6_4.jpg\" style=\"width: 617.99px; height: 842.927px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"http://cspi.uzz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/w.jpg\" style=\"width: 626.993px; height: 881.021px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tadbirni Prorektor B.E.Xusanov ochib berdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chirchiq davlat pedagogika instituti &nbsp;dotsent v.b.X.E.Sultanovning RANGTASVIR (Akvarelda natryumort ishalsh) o`quv qo`llanmasi “Tasviriy san’at va muhandislik grafikasi” ta’limi &nbsp;yo’nalishi uchun Rangtasvir-o`quv fani sifatida amaliy san’at yo`nalishlari &nbsp;mutaxassislik fanlar orasida asosiy o`rin e