(202, 'Tabriklaymiz!', 'tabriklaymiz', NULL, '<p align=\"right\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2019-%20yilgi/12.2019/photo_2019-12-19_22-20-11.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\">Ustoz – bu so‘z jarang sochganda, har kim turlicha ta’rif izlaydi. Buni qarangki, bu so‘zga dunyo lug‘atlarida ham bir xil ta’rif keltiriladi. Ya’nikim, ota kabi ulug‘, ona kabi sirdosh... Birinchi ustozimiz, o‘qishni, yozishni o‘rgatib, xat-savodimizni chiqaradi. Ulg‘ayganimiz sari, katta hayotning o‘zi bizga ustozlik qila boshlaydi. Aynan shu jarayonda yana murabbiylar, muallimlar qo‘lidan tutamiz. Ular bizga hayotning past-baland tepaliklaridan o‘tishimizda hamrohlik qiladi. Pand-nasihatlari, duolari bilan umr yo‘llarimizni xuddi shamchiroq kabi yoritadi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><em>\"Karvon uchun sarbon kerak, har qadamda...\"</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2017 yil. Toshkent viloyatida ishlab chiqarish, iqtisodiyot, turizm sohasi anchagina rivojlangan. Biroq, mamlakatimiz taraqqiyoti va kelajagini belgilab beradigan ta’lim tizimi boshqa viloyatlarga nisbatan past ko‘rsatgichlarni band etayotgan bir davr... Yurboshimizning sa’iy harakatlari bilan Chirchiq shahrida pedagogika oliygohi faoliyat boshlashi zarurligi e’tirof etilib, tegishli qonunlar qabul qilindi. Institut va institut rahbariyati oldiga yuksak vazifalar qo‘yildi... Qarabsizki, ilm karvoni yo‘lga chiqdi. Juda olis yo‘lga... Bu karvonga professor – G‘ofurjon Muhamedov sarbon etib tayinlandi. Ilm mashvaratini yoqqancha, karvon ortidan bir guruh pedagoglar jamoasi, 750 nafar talabalar ergashdi. Bu orada endigina rivojlanish tetapoyalaridan ko‘tarilayotgan shaharga madaniyat, ma’rifat, ilm-fan, bir so‘z bilan aytganda, \"sivilizatsiya\" nafasi &nbsp;kirib keldi. Tez orada bir-biridan ko‘rkam va muhtasham binolar qad rostladi...</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><em>2019 yil. 20-dekabr...</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bugun qutlug‘ kun! Ya’nikim, ustoz Muhamedov Gafurjon &nbsp;Isroilovich yaqinlari, bir guruh shogirdlari davrasida 70 yoshni qarshi olmoqda...</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><em>\"Har niholga bog‘bon kerak\"...</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umid bilan qadalgan nihollar bo‘y ko‘rsatdi. Ulg‘aydi, meva tugdi. Bog‘bon esa hali-hanuz yangi-yangi nihollar parvarishi bilan band. Ustoz, biz baralla ayta olamizki, &nbsp;Siz bugun Toshkent viloyatining “ilm-ziyo bog‘i”ga bog‘bonsiz. Necha yuzlab yozilajak ilmiy-tadqiqot ishlariga, minglab tarbiyalanajak farzandlar kelajagiga sarbonsiz...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ustoz, G‘ofurjon Isroilovich, bundan 3 yil avval siz yo‘l boshlagan karvon, &nbsp;ilmu ziyoga tashna qalblar orasida biz ham bor edik. Buni qarangki, bugun Sizni ustoz deb biladigan, Sizga suyanadigan, suhbatingizga doimo oshiqadigan &nbsp;shogirdlaringiz soni 9 mingtaga yetdi... Ularning har biri qalbida ertangi kun ishqi bilan yuksak pedagoglik maqomini oqlash ilinjida tinimsiz mehnat qilmoqda...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G‘ofurjon Isroilovich, Siz talabchan rahbar, mehribon ustoz, fayzli insonsiz! Kezi kelganda, qatiqqo‘l rahbar bo‘lib shogirdlarni tarbiyalayapsiz. Yuzingizdagi nur, iliq tabassum doimiy hamrohingiz, jonajon O‘zbekistonimizning ilmiy ravnaqi yo‘lidagi ezgu ishlaringizda esa ulkan zafarlar yor bo‘lsin!</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><em><strong>Institut axborot xizmati.</strong></em></p>', '2019-12-20 00:55:13', '1', 3641, '2019-12-20 00:55:13', '2021-01-07 01:48:59', '/2019- yilgi/12.2019/photo_2019-12-19_22-20-11.jpg', 1, NULL, 5, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(203, 'RUS TILI VA ADABIYOTI KAFEDRASIDA IJODIY UCHRASHUV...', 'rus-tili-va-adabiyoti-kafedrasida-ijodiy-uchrashuv', NULL, '<p>Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika instituti \"Tarix va tillar\" fakulteti “Rus tili va adabiyoti” kafedrasi tomonidan shoir, nasriy yozuvchi, publitsist, va tarjimon Bahodir Ahmedov bilan adabiy uchrashuv tashkil etildi. Uchrashuv davomida talabalar tomonidan shoirning ijodidan namunalar keltirildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2019-%20yilgi/12.2019/IMG_6794-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 67%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Bah (Bahodir) Ahmedovning ijod olamidagi erishgan yutuqlari haqida so‘z borganda, uning ijodi dunyoning boshqa mamlakatlari tillariga ham tarjima qilingan. Shu bilan birgalikda ijodkor, aniq fanlar sohasida ham muvafaqqiyatga erishgan. Fizika-matematika fanlari nomzodi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tashkil etilgan uchrashuv talaba-yoshlar uchun &nbsp;\"motivatsiya\" &nbsp;bera oldi.</p>', '2019-12-27 04:58:01', '1', 3507, '2019-12-27 04:58:01', '2020-12-31 14:36:50', '/2019- yilgi/12.2019/IMG_6795-min.jpg', 1, NULL, 5, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(204, 'XALOSKORSIZ OFAT KELSA BOG\'IMGA...', 'haloskorsiz-ofat-kelsa-bogimga', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tinch, osoyishta zaminda yashayotganligimizda chegarada sergak turgan mard va jasur o’glonlarimizning xizmatlari katta. Ular tinchlik va osoyishtaligimiz posbonlaridir…\r\n	<br>O‘zbekiston Respublikasi Qurolli kuchlari tashkil topganligining 28 yilligi hamda 14-yanvar – Vatan himoyachilari kuni munosabati bilan Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika institutida Vatanparvarlik – milliy yuksalish kafolati shiori ostida “Qo‘mondon va yoshlar” uchrashuvi tashkil etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0228-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0257-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Uchrashuvda Chirchiq shahrida joylashgan harbiy qism komandirlari, orkestor jamoasi, institut professor-o‘qituvchilari, talaba-yoshlar ishtirok etishdi va talabalar o’zlarini qiziqtirgan savollarga soha mutaxassislaridan javoblar olishdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0215-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0200-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0244-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0235-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>Ma’naviy-ma’rifiy tadbirda 2019-2020 o\'quv yili davomida ilmiy, ijodiy jarayonlarda faollik ko’rsatgan tashabbuskor yoshlar turli nominatsiyalarda institut yoshlar ittifoqi boshlang\'ich tashkilotining maxsus statuetkalari bilan taqdirlandi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0340-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0374-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>Tadbirning badiiy qismida qo‘mondonlikning orkestr jamoasi hamda institut musiqa ta’limi yo‘nalishi talabalari hamkorligida konsert dasturi namoyish etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0366-min.jpg\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 97%;\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0393-min.jpg\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 97%;\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>Institutda o’tkazilgan “Qo‘mondon va yoshlar” uchrashuvi barchada katta taassurot qoldirdi. Tadbir jarang sochgan kuy-qo’shiqlar sadosi ostida ko’tarinki kayfiyatda yakunlandi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0108-min.jpg\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 97%;\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/IMG_0193-min.jpg\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 97%;\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<br><strong>Institut axborot xizmati.</strong></p>', '2020-01-12 06:17:29', '1', 2307, '2020-01-13 01:30:49', '2020-12-21 10:53:33', '/2020-yilgi/IMG_0228-min.jpg', 2, NULL, 5, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(205, 'KASABA UYUSHMASIDA YANGI YIL SPARTAKIADASI', 'kasaba-uyushmasida-yangi-yil-spartakiadasi', NULL, '<p align=\"center\">O‘zbekiston ta’lim, fan va madaniyat hodimlari kasaba uyushmasi Chirchiq shahar Kengashi hamda Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika instituti &nbsp;Boshlang‘ich Kasaba uyushmasi tomonidan professor-o‘qituvchilar &nbsp;o‘rtasida yangi yil bayrami munosabati bilan <strong>“Yangi yil spartakiadasi”</strong> sport musobaqalari o‘tkazildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-2.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-4.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; O‘tkazilgan musobaqalar institut professor-o‘qituvchilari va hodimlari o‘rtasida o‘zaro hamjihatlikni mustahkamlash, sportni ommalashtirish orqali sog‘lom turmush tarzini targ‘ib qilishdan iborat bo‘lib, institutda professor-o‘qituvchilar va xodimlardan iborat sport jamoalarini shakllantiirish, muntazam sport bilan shug‘ullanishni tizimli amalga oshirish mexanizmlarini yaratish, institut jamoasini turli spartakiadalarga tayyorlash, faol ishtirokini ta’minlash kabi qator vazifalarni maqsad qilgan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shu munosabat bilan institutning barcha fakultetlarida sport musobaqalari o‘tkazildi. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-5.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Musobaqalarning taqdirlash marosimi 2019 yilning 29 dekabr kuni bayramona yasatilgan yangi yil dasturxoni atrofida o‘tkazildi. Tadbirda institut rektori –G‘.I.Muxamedov, Chirchiq shahar hokimi o‘rinbosari – J.Matkarimov ishtirok etishdi. Tadbirda sport musobaqalari yakuni bo‘yicha TVChDPI kasaba uyushmasi raisi D.Zakirovning kichik xisoboti tinglandi hamda musobaqa g‘oliblari va nominantlarga O‘zbekiston ta’lim, fan va madaniyat xodimlari kasaba uyushmasi Chirchiq shahar Kengashi tomonidan ta’sis etilgan qimmatbaho sovrin va sport anjomlari taqdim etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-11.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-10.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shuningdek, musobaqani o‘tkazishda hakamlik qilgan, tashkiliy va uslubiy jihatdan asosiy ko‘makni tashkil etgan “Jismoniy madaniyat” kafedrasining 9 nafar o‘qituvchi va murabbiylariga esdalik sovg‘alari topshirildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-12.jpg\" style=\"width: 90%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/Sport%20yangiliklari-9.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika instituti boshlang‘ich kasaba uyushmasi 2020 yilda ham institut professor-o‘qituvchilari va xodimlari o‘rtasida o‘zaro hamjihatlikni mustahkamlash hamda sportni ommalashtirish orqali sog‘lom turmush tarzini targ‘ib qilishni davom ettiradi...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>Institut axborot xizmati.</strong></p>', '2020-01-14 06:28:50', '1', 2451, '2020-01-14 06:28:50', '2021-01-06 16:12:53', '/2020-yilgi/01 yanvar/Sport yangiliklari-11.jpg', 1, NULL, 13, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(206, 'INSTITUTDA “REKTOR VA YOSHLAR” UCHRASHUVI', 'chdpida-rektor-va-yoshlar-uchrashuvi', NULL, '<p>Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika institutida “Rektor va yoshlar” uchrashuvi bo‘lib o‘tdi. Unda institut rektori G‘. I. Muhamedov, soha prorektorlari va “Maktabgacha va boshlang‘ich ta’lim”, “Pedagogika” fakultetlarining talaba-yoshlari ishtirok etishdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/IMG_0180-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/IMG_0174-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uchrashuv davomida talaba-yoshlarga minbar berildi. &nbsp;Talabalar o‘zlarining taklif, mulohaza va savollari bilan institut rahbariyat jamoasiga murojaat qilish imkoniyatiga ega bo‘lishdi. &nbsp;Savollarga institut rektori va prorektorlari tomonidan &nbsp;javoblar berildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>“Pedagogika” fakulteti, Maktab menedjmenti yo‘nalishi talabasi tomonidan quyidagicha savol berildi:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>– Men Maktab menedjmenti yo‘nalishida tahsil olaman. Yo‘nalishimizda asosiy e’tibor boshqaruv tizimiga qaratiladi. Lekin biz o‘qishni bitirgan zahoti boshqaruv tizimida ishlay olmaymiz, buning uchun bizda ish staji &nbsp;va tajriba bo‘lishi kerak, shu sababdan, bizning yo‘nalishimizga qo‘shimcha yo‘nalish kiritilish imkoniyati bormi?</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>O‘rinli taklif. Bu masala bo‘yicha &nbsp;Oliy ta’lim vazirligiga tavsiya beramiz.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Savol-javob va muhokamalar shu tarzda olib borildi...</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/IMG_0201-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/IMG_0200-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shu hafta davomida <strong>“Rektor va yoshlar”</strong> uchrashuvi institutning boshqa fakultetlarida ham davom etadi...</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>Institut axborot xizmati.&nbsp;</strong></p>', '2020-01-16 08:06:27', '1', 2874, '2020-01-16 08:06:27', '2021-01-07 02:31:04', '/2020-yilgi/01 yanvar/IMG_0174-min.jpg', 2, NULL, 5, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(207, 'PROKUROR VA YOSHLAR UCHRASHUVI', 'prokuror-va-yoshlar-uchrashuvi', NULL, '<p>Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika institutida <strong>“Prokuror va yoshlar”</strong> uchrashuvi bo‘lib o‘tdi. Unda Chirchiq shahar prokurori, Chirchiq shahar soliq inspeksiyasi hamda Prezident qabulxonasi Chirchiq shahar bo‘limi vakillari, institut rektori, talaba-yoshlar &nbsp;ishtirok etishdi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uchrashuv savol-javob, ochiq muloqot tarzida olib borildi. Talabalar o‘zlarini qiziqtirgan siyosiy, iqtisodiy va ma’naviy ma’rifiy hayotga oid savollariga mutaxassislardan javoblar olishdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo2020-01-1812-20-41-2.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-18_12-20-44.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Uchrashuv davomida Chirchiq shahar prokurori, Adliya katta maslahatchisi – Baxtiyor Ibrohimov</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shaharda pedagogika instituti ochilishi, Ziyolilarning soni ko‘payishi orqali shaharda jinoyatchiliklar soni kamayishiga erishilganligi, &nbsp;endi shaharda Oliy ma’lumotli mutaxassislar kontingentini ko‘paytirish kerakligini alohida, ta’kidlab o‘tdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Bundan tashqari, institut talabalari tomonidan berilgan ko‘plab taklif-mulohazalar ma’qullandi. Talabalar tomonidan Chirchiq shahrida abiturientlarni Oliy o‘quv yurtiga tayyorlash markazi faoliyatini yo‘lga qo‘yish hamda mana shu muassasada talabalar faoliyat olib borishi taklifi berildi. Bu taklif bir ovozdan qo‘llab-quvvatlandi. &nbsp;Mazkur taklif yuzasidan Chirchiq shahar prokurori, Yoshlar ittifoqi shahar Kengashi, institut jamoasi birgalikda ish olib borishga kelishib olindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-18_12-20-42.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo2020-01-1812-20-41-2.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uchrashuv so‘ngida,<strong>&nbsp;</strong>talabalar tomonidan berilgan savollar anchagina zalvorli ekanligi aytib o‘tildi. Bunday uchrashuvlarning tashkil etilishi yangi maqsad, taklif va rejalar bilan maydonga chiqayotgan yoshlarni kashf qilishga, ularning qiziqish va xohishlarini to‘g‘ri yo‘naltirishga xizmat qiladi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Qiziqarli bahs-munozaralarga boy bo‘lgan uchrashuv ko‘tarinki kayfiyatda yakunlandi.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>Institut axborot xizmati.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>', '2020-01-20 06:39:17', '1', 2719, '2020-01-20 06:39:17', '2021-01-06 17:17:37', '/2020-yilgi/01 yanvar/photo_2020-01-18_12-20-43.jpg', 1, NULL, 5, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(208, 'TASVIRIY SAN’AT KAFEDRASI TOMONIDAN  BEKOBOD TUMANIDAGI UMUMTA’LIM MAKTABIDA  MAHORAT DARSLARI TASHKIL ETILDI', 'pedagogik-talim-innovatsion-klasteri-talim-va-tarbiya-uzviyligi', NULL, '<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>“Sport va chaqiriqqacha harbiy ta’lim” fakulteti, Tasviriy san’at kafedrasi professor-o‘qituvchilari tomonidan Bekobod tumanida joylashgan 29-umumta’lim maktabida iqtidorli yoshlarni aniqlash, o‘quvchilarning san’atga qiziqishlarini oshirish maqsadida “Pedagogik ta’lim innovatsion klasteri” bo‘yicha hamkorlik doirasidagi ijodiy ko‘rgazma va iqtidorli talabalarning mahorat darslari o‘tkazildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Tadbirda Chirchiq davlat pedagogika instituti, tasviriy san’at kafedrasi professor-o‘qituvchi va talaba-yoshlari ishtirok etishdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-33-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\">\r\n					<br>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-28-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-52-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-08-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tadbir doirasida “Tasviriy sa’nat va muhandislik grafikasi” ta’lim yo‘nalishi talabalarining ijodiy asarlari ko‘rgazmasi tashkil etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mahorat darslari davomida institutning asosiy strategik g‘oyasi bo‘lgan – “Pedagogik ta’lim innovatsion klasteri”ning asosiy mazmun-mohiyati xususida ma’lumotlar berilib, “maktab laboratoriyasi”da olib borilayotgan ishlar taqdimoti namoyish etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-49-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-28-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Ta’lim muassasasiga kafedra tomonidan metodik yordam ko‘rsatildi hamda tadbirda faol ishtirok etgan ishtirokchilarga esdalik sovg‘alari berildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-41-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-15-min.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\">\r\n				<br>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2020-01-24 07:20:11', '1', 2111, '2020-01-24 07:30:08', '2021-01-07 03:53:46', '/2020-yilgi/01 yanvar/photo_2020-01-24_17-23-12-min.jpg', 1, NULL, 18, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(209, 'TASVIRIY SAN’AT YO’NALISHIDA “PEDAGOGIK TA’LIM INNOVATSION KLASTERI” ISTIQBOLLARI', 'tasviriy-san-yonalishida-pedagogik-talim-innovatsion-klasteri-istiqbollari', NULL, '<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">“Tasviriy san’at” kafedrasida hamkor muassasalar bilan “Pedagogik ta’lim innovatsion klasteri” yuzasidan fikr-almashinuv seminari tashkil etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"margin-right: calc(0%); width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/yangiliktasviriy_1.jpg\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 97%;\"></td>\r\n			<td><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/yangiliktasviriy_5.jpg\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 97%;\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seminarda &nbsp;“Maktab-laboratoriya” innovatsion tajriba maydonchalarini tashkil qilish va samaradorligini oshirish bo‘yicha uslubiy qo‘llanma muallifi –U.Xo‘jamqulov hamda Qibray tumanidagi umumta’lim maktablarining tasviriy san’at va chizmachilik fani o’qituvchilari, &nbsp;2-bolalar musiqa va san’at maktabi amaliy san’at bo‘limi, “Sharq miniatyura” yo‘nalishi to‘garagi, amaliy san’at yog‘och o‘ymakorligi to‘garagi o‘qituvchilari faol ishtirok etishdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/yangiliktasviriy_6.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/yangiliktasviriy_4.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mutaxassislar tomonidan sohaga oid istiqbolli rejalar muhokama qilindi. “Pedagogik ta’lim innovatsion klasteri”ning Qibray tumani maktablaridagi faoliyati hamda aynan tasviriy san’at yo’nalishida olib borilayotgan ishlar samaradorligini oshirish maqsadida tashkil etilgan ushbu seminar mutaxassislarning tajriba almashishlari uchun qulay imkoniyat yaratdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\">&nbsp;<strong>Institut axborot xizmati.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>', '2020-01-26 07:23:53', '1', 2291, '2020-01-26 07:23:53', '2021-01-06 14:48:43', '/2020-yilgi/yangiliktasviriy_1.jpg', 1, NULL, 5, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(210, 'INSTITUTDA ISSIQXONA BARPO ETILDI...', 'institutda-issiqxona-barpo-etildi', NULL, '<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Oliy ta’lim tizimida talaba-yoshlarning egallagan nazariy bilimlarini amaliyotda qo‘llay olish ko‘nikma va malakalarini hamda kasbiy kompetensiyalarini rivojlantirishda amaliy mashg‘ulotlarning o‘rni juda katta. Shu nuqtai-nazardan “Tabiiy fanlar” fakulteti binosi atrofidagi foydalanilmayotgan yer maydonida biologik-genetik-seleksion tadqiqotlar olib borish hamda o‘quv-tajriba mashg‘ulotlarini mavsumdan tashqari vaqtlarda o‘tkazish, ta’lim va fan samaradorligini oshirish maqsadida  zamonaviy <strong>issiqxona </strong>barpo etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-28_15-55-53.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">\r\n				<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-28_15-55-49.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Issiqxonaning yarmiga sitrus  o‘simliklar – limon, mandarin, apelsin, papayya (qovun daraxti) ular oralig‘iga ko‘katlar – kashnich, ukrop qolgan yarmiga rediska, bodringning qishki navi hamda bir va ko‘p yillik gullar urug‘lari va  boshqa o‘simliklar ko‘chatlari ekilib,  kuzatuv hamda amaliy mashg‘ulotlar olib borilmoqda.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-28_15-55-51.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-28_15-55-44.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Talabalarda yopiq tomorqa xo‘jaliklaridan unumli foydalanish, mavsumiy davrlarda o‘simliklarni o‘stirish maqsadida himoyalangan yer maydonlari qurish ishlarini o‘rganish, ekindan yuqori hosil olishda oziqlantirish me’yorlari, usullari haqida tasavvur, ko‘nikma, malaka va kompetensiyalarga ega bo‘lishi e’tiborga olingan bo‘lib, <strong>“</strong><strong>Tomorqa xo‘jaligini tashkil etish”</strong> fanini o‘qitish rejalashtirilgan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mazkur fan asosida “Biologiya o‘qitish metodikasi” va “Kimyo o‘qitish metodikasi” hamda barcha ta’lim yo‘nalishlar talabalarini o‘qitish ko‘zda tutildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Institut axborot xizmati.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">          </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>', '2020-01-28 05:57:00', '1', 3870, '2020-01-28 06:00:24', '2021-01-06 15:48:09', '/2020-yilgi/01 yanvar/photo_2020-01-28_15-55-49.jpg', 1, NULL, 5, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
(211, 'PROKUROR SEKTORIDA: “5 MUHIM TASHABBUS” LOYIHASI G‘OLIBLARI TAQDIRLANDI', 'prokuror-sektorida-5-muhim-tashbbus-loyihasi-goliblari-taqdirlandi', NULL, '<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika institutining malakali prfessor-o‘qituvchilari Chirchiq shahridagi umumta’lim maktablari, mehribonlik uyiga biriktirilib, “5 muhim tashabbus” doirasida turli to‘garaklar tashkil qilindi. Mazkur ta’lim muassasalarda “Innovatsion ta’lim klasteri” asosida turli sport musobaqalari, qolaversa, yoshlarni kompyuter texnologiyalaridan samarali foydalanishini tashkil etish maqsadida turli musobaqalar, master-klass mashg‘ulotlari, o‘quv-seminarlar o‘tkazilib kelinmoqda...</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/photo_2020-01-30_08-45-50.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-30_08-45-53.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-30_08-46-01.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-30_08-45-58.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chirchiq davlat pedagogika institutida “5 muhim tashabbus” doirasida o‘tkazilgan tadbirlarda faol ishtirok etib, g‘oliblikni qo‘lga kiritgan yoshlarni taqdirlash marosimi bo‘lib o‘tdi. Unda Chirchiq shahar prokurori, Ichki ishlar bosh Boshqarmasi boshlig‘i, shahar soliq inspeksiyasi boshlig‘i, hokimlik vakillari hamda shahardagi umumta’lim maktablari o‘quvchilari, 14-sonli mehribonlik uyi tarbiyalanuvchilari, talaba-yoshlar ishtirok etishdi. Tadbir davomida “5 muhim tashabbus”ning har bir yo‘nalishida o‘tkazilgan ko‘rik-tanlov va sport musobaqalarida peshqadamlik qilgan o‘quvchi va talaba-yoshlar turli nominatsiyalar bo‘yicha taqdirlanishdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-30_08-46-04.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/01%20yanvar/photo_2020-01-30_08-46-07.jpg\" style=\"width: 97%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shuningdek, institut qoshida “Yosh kitobxonlar klubi” tashkil etilib, mazkur klubga “Yosh kitobxon” ko‘rik-tanlovining respublika bosqichi g‘olibi, 21-umumta’lim maktabi o‘quvchisi Otabek Eshpo‘latov yetakchi etib saylandi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uchrashuv davomida Chirchiq shahar prokurori, Adliya katta maslahatchisi – Baxtiyor Ibrohimov g‘oliblarni taqdirlar ekan, joriy yilda 4 ta sektor homiyligida shahardagi adabiyot va she’riyatga qiziqishi bor, iqtidorli yoshlarning ijod namunalari aks etgan to‘plam kitobini nashr ettirish taklifini bildirdi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tadbirda institut talabalari tomonidan sahnalashtirilgan “Ortepa” spektakli namoyish etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Institut axborot xizmati.</strong></p>', '2020-01-29 22:54:09', '1', 3944, '2020-01-29 22:54:09', '2021-01-07 01:44:04', '/2020-yilgi/01 yanvar/photo_2020-01-30_08-46-04.jpg', 1, NULL, 6, 0, '', 1, NULL, '', '', '', '');
