(262, '“Abdulla Qahhor – mohir hikoyanavis” mavzusida o’tkazilgan adabiy kecha', 'abdulla-qahhor-mohir-hikoyanavis-mavzusida-otkazilgan-adabiy-kecha', NULL, '<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>17 sentabr – ulug‘ adib, mohir “so‘z zargari” Abdulla Qahhor tavalludining 113 yilligi munosabati bilan Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq davlat pedagogika institutida “<strong>Abdulla Qahhor – mohir hikoyanavis</strong>” mavzusida onlayn adabiy seminar tashkil etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/09%20sentiyabr/test-test1-manaviyat.jpg\" style=\"width: 80%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adabiy seminar institut yoshlar bilan ishlash, ma’naviyat va ma’rifat bo‘limi hamda Tarix va tillar fakulteti, O‘zbek tili va adabiyoti kafedrasi hamkorligida tashkil etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/09%20sentiyabr/test-test1-manaviyat-2.jpg\" style=\"width: 80%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ZOOM platformasi orqali tashkil etilgan ushbu tadbirda Jizzax davlat pedagogika instituti, O’zbekiston davlat jismoniy tarbiya va sport universiteti, Toshkent texnika universiteti Olmaliq filiali, Toshkent davlat agrar universitetining professor o’qituvchilari, Abdulla Qahhor uy muzeyi xodimlari hamda institut talabalari ishtirok etdilar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.cspi.uz/storage/app/media/2020-yilgi/09%20sentiyabr/test-test1-manaviyat-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 80%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>O‘zbek adabiyoti va madaniyati rivojiga ulkan hissa qo‘shgan atoqli adib, O‘zbekiston Xalq yozuvchisi Abdulla Qahhorning ijodiy merosi yosh avlodni Vatanga muhabbat va sadoqat, milliy va umuminsoniy qadriyatlar ruhida tarbiyalash borasida &nbsp;muhim ahamiyatga ega.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<!--[if !vml]-->\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>', '2020-09-17 05:13:50', '1', 53780, '2020-09-17 05:14:11', '2021-01-07 03:53:44', '/2020-yilgi/09 sentiyabr/test-test1-manaviyat.jpg', 1, NULL, 18, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, '', '', '', ''),
